Fiesta Salsa*: Combine all of the Fiesta Salsa* ingredients in a small bowl; set aside. Cinco de Layer Dip: Stir together the beans and taco seasoning mix until well blended; spread into the bottom of a 13x9-inch dish. Top with guacamole and cheese. Stir together the sour cream and chipotle peppers in a small bowl; carefully spread over the cheese. Drain any juices from the salsa and spoon over the chipotle cream. Serve immediately with tortilla chips.